免。<br />\n<br />\n而進入校園留守嘅手足，在場嘅都係戰友，武力係用嚟對付出面嘅仆街政權，意見不合，大家可以各有各做，互相尊重，毋忘保衞校園嘅初衷，一啲可能會損毀校園嘅行為，非必要情況下亦可以適量減少。<br />\n<br />\n至於其他長期受到高壓嘅前線戰友，呢兩日不妨可以放低一下，好好畀自己叉下電。張馳有道，先可以收放自如。<br />\n<br />\n另外亦希望喺出面開指責 post 嘅朋友，以建議代替指責，用諒解化解對立。大家目標一致，抗戰成功日，煲底相見時。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oKae8oV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoKae8oV.jpg&h=2c70cdea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後要再一次感激五個月嚟，一齊經歷過無數次槍林彈雨，挨過咗無數指罵恐嚇，抵受過無窮壓力嘅所有戰友。<br />\n<br />\n一齊撐落去，多謝你哋每一位！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:32:17.000Z","msg":"曱近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T02:34:13.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:04:34.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj